title: The florist
description: This project is designed for the flower shop. It enables shop owners to sell their products as well as advertise their services and products.I developed this web application to put my React skills into practice

title: 24/7 GYM
description: The 24/7 gym website is a responsive static website made with Webflow. This website aims to reach its audience and provide relevant information about the 24/7 gym. It provides detailed information about the gym and its facilities.

title: MetaCare hub
description: The platform aims to empower disabled individuals by providing a user-friendly interface and reliable assistance options. It incorporates features such as secure communication channels and customizable preferences to enhance the user experience and meet diverse needs.

title: Why Why Waste
description: This application is developed to reduce food insecurity among the common people, as well as to reduce food waste. The app allows eatery owners to list their leftover foods at the end of the day for a reduced price.
